    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in pristine showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. Meticulously maintained and displaying an immaculate aesthetic both internally and externally, it offers an unrivaled driving experience for the discerning buyer. Every detail reflects a standard of care that preserves its original integrity, ensuring it remains an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence. We invite serious inquiries to appreciate this peerless offering in person.",
      "price": 48500.0,
